Directed by Devesh Pratap Singh

Written by Rachel Singh

Cast Meeraj Shah(Neel). Sakshi Singh(Mini). Avtar Singh Bhullar (Jai). Sadia Nabila (Reena). Kp Sandhu (Rocky). Pankaj Kumar (Raja Bhai). King Chouhan (Veer). Pallavi Sharma (Maya Devi). Rashmi Ravindran (Rhea). Guru Dha (Gangster). Dave Sidhu (Rohan)

Languages Hindi

Producers Guru Dha. Rachel Singh

Production AJ Films Entertainment World. Dreamz Production
